lead_paragraph: FIFA presidential candidate Prince Ali Bin Al Hussein has appealed to sport's highest tribunal over his request for  transparent voting booths and independent scrutineers at Friday's election for the head of the global soccer body.

headline.print_headline: Jordan's Prince Ali Calls for Delay in FIFA Vote, Appeals to CAS
